Package pkgMain

Class DesignGardenView

java.lang.Object
pkgMain.View
pkgMain.AddPlantsView
pkgMain.DesignGardenView
public class DesignGardenView
extends AddPlantsView
Class - DesignGardenView, the view for the main scene of the application. This displays the garden and the tabs for all the plants. Gives the options for the users to save their garden, visit the plant bank, save the garden, and go back to the opening scene.
Author:
William Cantera, Diane Vinson, Ben Testani, Jacob Kuchma, Maria Venrooy
